## One Easy-to-Use Platform for Assisted Living
### ECP Move-Ins
Track Every Step—From First Tour to Move-In Day—All in One Place
Move residents in faster, increase occupancy, and create a better family experience with ECP Move-Ins—the all-in-one solution for managing every step of the admissions process effortlessly.

## Senior Living eMAR
Reduced med errors, improved oversight, happier residents
Improve med-passing workflows, ensure accurate med administration, and prioritize resident safety. Connect to your pharmacy for enhanced care coordination - all in a single user-friendly platform.

## Senior Living EHR and Care Plans
Easier charting, better care, happier residents
Complete assessments, automatically build care plans and generate task lists, track incidents and more. Enjoy better outcomes, longer stays, and happier residents.

