## Senior Living CRM
Capture leads, grow occupancy, move in happy residents
It's all possible with our all-in-one, user-friendly platform. Welcome to ECP CRM, where you can capture leads instantly, connect and build relationships, and make the move-in process simple.

## Senior Living Billing Software
Happy families and residents: it starts with accurate billing
Capture revenue in real-time as charges flow automatically from Clinical directly into Billing - all within a single user-friendly platform. This means fewer errors, less stress for your team, and increased revenue for your business.

